import React from "react";

import "./CardsPrin.css";


function CardsPrin() {
  return (

    <
    div >
    <
    h2 class = "text-center m-4" > NUESTROS PRODUCTOS < /h2>

    <
    Card img = "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1448932223592-d1fc686e76ea"
    title = "Computadores" /
    >
    <
    Card img = "./assets/impresoras.jpg"
    title = "Impresoras" /
    >

    <
    /div>



  );
}

function Card(props) {
  return ( <
    div >
    <
    div class = "contenedor  " >
    <
    div class = "contenedor-cards  " >
    <
    div class = "contenedor-card-item  " >
    <
    p class = "tittle text-center" > {
      props.title
    } < /p> <
    div class = "contenedor-card-item-wrapper" >
    <
    img src = {
      props.img
    }
    alt = "" / >
    <
    div class = "contenedor-info" >
    <
    div class = "info" >
    <
    button type = "button "
    class = "btn btn-warning" > Ver mas < /button> <
    /div> <
    div class = "fondo" > < /div> <
    /div> <
    /div> <
    /div>          <
    /div> <
    /div> <
    /div>

  );
}
export default CardsPrin;
